survey_response.review_text: Writing this review after visiting many dentists over the past 15 years or so in and around Nerul and Seawoods. I recently took my wife to this dental clinic, and our experience was outstanding. From start to finish, the process was smooth, and the dentist handled the root canal with exceptional ease and confidence. The care and expertise demonstrated were truly impressive. We highly recommend this clinic for top-notch dental services. Five stars without a doubt!
Right from first consultation  to the procedure it was efficient professional approach  of the Doctor.

Regarding Dr. Chaitali, I am quite pleased. Her treatment of dental-related issues is visited by our entire family. Her proficiency as a dentist is remarkable. I really believe that people should see Dr. Chaitali.

Befire going to doctor , i had fear about this paiinful procedure due to my past experiences with other doctors. 

But with this madam i got Awsome Experience,  in first visit docor started root canal procedure. Entire procedure was of 45 mins with zero pain. I am very happy. After procedure she also gave me scientific  explanations , dos and donts for and during implant procedure.  I immediately decided to go for Implant orocedure with same doctor. 

I strongly recommend this doctor.

Dr. Chaitali is a very professional and experienced doctor. Have done my teeth extraction and root canal there, the procedure were smooth and treatment was not painful. Definitely a yes for dental treatment. Caring, polite and punctual. Gives detailed explanation to your queries. Happy with her treatment.

Took my dad for consultation. He had tooth ache. Waiting time was less. She quickly gave diagnosis and suggested filling. We didn't have to take another appointment, she got it done right away within half hour. She was gentle and sensitive. Dad is usually scared of dental treatments, but this time he was quite comfortable and relaxed as she took him through the process sensitively and explained well patiently. Dad is very happy with the treatment and the issue was solved perfectly. Thank you.

Dr. Chaitali is a very professional and experienced Dentist. Her calm demeanour and pleasant personality puts the patient at ease right at the beginning. She is very clear in her opinion about the patients condition, and lays out the facts without ambiguity. She is easy to talk to and discuss the problems without inhibitions. My family and I have sought her consultation regularly, and we highly recommend her.
